cdata.name: Camcoin
cdata.desc: CamCoin has an open libertarian philosophy on sharing photography and art. It is a PoW PoS hybrid X11 based alternative crypto currency with a block time of 60 seconds and difficulty retargetting every 20 blocks. There was  a small premine of 10,000 CAM on a total supply of 10 million - The PoS rate is 9%.
